<item>
            <title>[WFLY-1810] SFSB tx lock not released in exception was thrown in Synchronization callback</title>
                <link>https://issues.jboss.org/browse/WFLY-1810</link>
                <project id="12313721" key="WFLY">WildFly</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because the owning tx was never pushed into the OwnableReentrantLock ownership stack in org.jboss.as.ejb3.component.stateful.StatefulSessionSynchronizationInterceptor.handleThrowableInTxSync(...).&lt;br/&gt;
This will cause subsequent Lock.tryAcquire(..) to fail for a different tx.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
